1.0.0.3.description:
Klevu adds semantically enriched nuances to your product catalog, including&#xD;
conceptual categories, relative terms, text and measurement normalizations&#xD;
and contextual relevance. As a result, when shoppers search on your store,&#xD;
even if the searched keywords do&#xD;
not match with catalog description, Klevu&#xD;
will provide relevant recommendations.
